       fhir:description [ fhir:v "A prescription for a radiotherapy treatment phase.\r\nIn ARIA, a prescription can cover a single plan or complete phase implemented with one or multiple plans. During prescription it may not even be defined whether\r\nmultiple plans will be used. Therefore, all ARIA prescriptions are exposed as Phase Prescriptions." ] ;
